title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 6 2022
description:
Doocy nails KJP on questioning the 2016 election. Biden rips MAGA Republicans again. Jennifer Lawrence says she dreams about Tucker Carlson. C&B break down the state of the senate races. Mollie Hemingway, senior editor at The Federalist and Fox News contributor joins Clay and Buck with some midterm election prognostications. Clay and Buck rank their favorite old school video games.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
